        <Parent_String>halls (interior rooms) [300004420], interior spaces (spaces by location) [300078790], rooms and spaces by location or context [300004011], rooms and spaces [300133704], built work divisions [300072553], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
